L-Laura-chan...!? Well, the weather is nice today, isn't it?
Ahaha...

U-Um, that's right... I'll give you a little allowance.
Please take it without saying anything.
Ugh... I'm such a terrible person...

It's river fish. Hatayaki Village can catch high-quality
fish from the nearby rivers.

These tomatoes were sourced from the 'Yuriseen' game. They
have become a 'petit boom' in Hatayaki Village.

\SE[15] Oh, you haven't left yet. \SE[15] Be careful, it's
dangerous outside the village.
